Account Size: $10,000
Risk Per Trade: 10% of equity
Commission: 0.1% per trade
These settings are designed to reflect practical trading scenarios and provide more accurate backtesting results. Feel free to adjust these parameters to match your trading preferences or market conditions. Remember, backtest results may vary based on asset, timeframe, and slippage. Happy trading! 🚀
